column6: CF Cooper Hammer Drill Bit SDS 4mm
column16:
CF Cooper SDS Hammer Drill Bits offer outstanding advantages on cost vs performance.
For use on rotary Hammer Drills designed for SDS shanks
1. Ideal for concrete and masonry, they can also be used on granite and other general construction materials.
2. The unique diamond ground carbide tip with its extra hard, thicker and more robust construction can help to drill faster and into even very hard concrete effortlessly.
3. Highly efficient flutes makes dust extraction faster and into even very hard concrete effortlessly.
4. Highly efficient flutes makes dust extraction faster thus providing a smooth and versatile drive and penetration into the drilling surface.

column6: Herman Premium Tomato Ketchup Glass Bottle 340 gram
column16:
Herman is a our flagship brand and encompasses a wide range of ever growing FMCG products with high Quality, value for money recipes which give them a strong international & universal appeal. The HERMAN product range includes Premium Mayonnaise & Tomato Ketchup, Regular Mayonnaise, & Tomato ketchup, Speciality and Ethnic Sauces, Vinegar, Hot sauce, Salad dressing, Pasta & Pizza sauce, Fish & Soya sauce, Yellow Mustard, Tomato Paste, Rose Syrup and Fruit Cordials The Dry products range includes Semolina, White oats, Corn flour and Glucose Powder, Custard Powder, Cake Mixes, Jelly, Cream Caramel..
The range comes in popular packaging conveniences well accepted across all markets.
Herman brand also provides most of the key products in Food Service packaging options to meet their demand of bulk buying of Quality products at reasonable price as consumables for the business. This included Sachets in Mayonnaise, Ketchup, Salad Dressings, Mustard & Tartar Sauce.

column6: Glass Keyboard KB01X
column16: The Q-gadget KB01 is a designer clear keyboard that is made from glass. The KB01 is not just a keyboard though, switching to touchpad mode allows you to use the entire area as a touchpad negating the need for a mouse. Switching between keyboard mode and touchpad mode is as simple as touching the switching button. The keyboard layout supports both Mac and Windows. The flat glass design means it is easy to wipe clean and there is no need to worry about dust getting in between the keys. Included in the box is an official cleaning cloth and an official USB cable with the UPQ logo.

column6: Q-music HDP5 BG(Headphone)
column16: Q-music HDP5 are wired/wireless foldable headphones with Bluetooth 4.0 and a battery that can last for up to 14 hours of wireless use. Closed headphones are perfect for use on a train or in the office, as you can listen at any volume without disturbing others. For comfortable, extended use large, soft ear pads are used to fully cover your ears. Inexpensive headphones tend to emphasize the bass sound and it leads to kill the high pitch sounds. Q-music HDP5 avoids excessive boosting on bass sound to let you enjoy the middle ranged sounds like vocal or guitar sounds, which makes it more like monitor headphones. There is less delay while using it as wireless headphone since aptX enabled. For a scene like playing game, where a little delay must be avoided, you can connect the cable to use it as a wired headphone. This is useful when the battery run out. *Please use the attached 3.5mm cable Microphone is installed inside the earpiece. You can use it as wireless headset when you receive call. You can adjust the volume with the up/down button, so you dont need to take out your smartphone to change the volume.
